#, no-c-format
msgid "255,0,0"
msgstr "255,0,0"

#. Tag: userinput
#: glossary.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "150,0,0"
msgstr "150,0,0"

#. Tag: userinput
#: glossary.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "0,255,0"
msgstr "0,255,0"

#. Tag: entry
#: glossary.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "green"
msgstr "žalia"

#. Tag: userinput
#: glossary.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "0,0,255"
msgstr "0,0,255"

#. Tag: entry
#: glossary.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "blue"
msgstr "mėlyna"

#. Tag: userinput
#: glossary.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "0,255,255"
msgstr "0,255,255"

#. Tag: entry
#: glossary.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "light blue"
msgstr "šviesiai mėlyna"

#. Tag: userinput
#: glossary.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "255,0,255"
msgstr "255,0,255"

#. Tag: entry
#: glossary.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "pink"
msgstr "rausva"

#. Tag: userinput
#: glossary.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "255,255,0"
msgstr "255,255,0"

#. Tag: entry
#: glossary.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "yellow"
msgstr "geltona"

#. Tag: para
#: glossary.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two commands need an RGB combination as input: these commands are "
"<userinput>canvascolor</userinput> and <userinput>pencolor</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Yra dvi komandos, kurioms kaip argumentą reikia nurodyti RŽM kombinaciją, "
"tai <userinput>keisk_foną</userinput> ir <userinput>pieštuko_spalva</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: glossterm
#: glossary.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "sprite"
msgstr "spruklys"

#. Tag: para
#: glossary.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A sprite is a small picture that can be moved around the screen. Our beloved "
"turtle, for instance, is a sprite."
msgstr ""
"Spruklys tai nedidelis paveikslėlis, kuris gali judėti ekrane. Pavyzdžiui, "
"ekrane matomas vėžliukas yra spruklys."

#. Tag: para
#: glossary.docbook:142
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note: with this version of &kturtle; the sprite cannot be changed from a "
#| "turtle into something else. Future versions of &kturtle; will be able to "
#| "do this."
msgid ""
"With this version of &kturtle; the sprite cannot be changed from a turtle "
"into something else. Future versions of &kturtle; will be able to do this."
msgstr ""
"Pastaba: šios laidos &kturtle; programoje vėžliuko spruklį neis pakeisti į "
